Package: groupedBBMH
Type: Package
Title: Grouped Beta-Binomial Model Using Metropolis-Hastings Estimation
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person(
      given = "Anonymous",
      family = "Anonymous",
      email = "Anonymous@gmail.com",
      role = c("aut", "cre"),
      comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0000-0000-0000")
    )
  )
Description: Provides tools for analyzing group testing data using 
    a truncated beta-binomial model with Metropolis-Hastings (MH) 
    and maximum-likelihood estimation (MLE) methods. The package 
    supports modeling imperfect test sensitivity and specificity, 
    estimating prevalence from grouped samples, and visualizing 
    posterior distributions.
